# 🧠 TDS Virtual TA – IITM Data Science Project

This is a virtual Teaching Assistant for the *Tools in Data Science* course. It uses embeddings + Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) to answer student questions based on course content and forum discussions.

---

## 🚀 Features

- ✅ FastAPI-powered backend
- ✅ Semantic search with FAISS
- ✅ Image OCR with pytesseract (base64 screenshots)
- ✅ Prompt-based LLM responses with link context
- ✅ Compatible with Promptfoo testing

---

